### Issue 3: "Too many edges (graph is cluttered)"
**Solution:** Use progressive disclosure
```javascript
// Only show edges for selected node
const activeEdges = selectedNode 
  ? edges.filter(e => e.source === selectedNode || e.target === selectedNode)
  : [];
```

